01:31:13,042 --> 01:31:15,500
<i>My destiny</i>

1098
01:31:15,583 --> 01:31:17,958
<i>Lies in your hands</i>

1099
01:31:18,042 --> 01:31:22,333
<i>We will never be apart</i>

