She left the house
and sent the little girl

1148
01:37:52,167 --> 01:37:54,667
<i>to tell Rishu to lock the door.</i>

1149
01:37:55,167 --> 01:37:57,250
Munni, tell Rishu to lock the door.

1150
01:37:57,333 --> 01:37:58,667
-Rishu!
<i>-But, sir,</i>

1151
01:37:58,750 --> 01:38:00,458
<i>Munni has testified </i>

1152
01:38:00,542 --> 01:38:02,375
<i>that Neel closed the door. </i>

1153
01:38:05,042 --> 01:38:06,125
Call the rickshaw driver.

1154
01:38:06,208 --> 01:38:08,208
Hey, you, come here. Quick!

1155
01:38:09,208 --> 01:38:10,917
-Tell him everything.
-Tell him.

1156
01:38:11,000 --> 01:38:15,958
Sir, madam was with me
from 3:15 p.m. to 4:15 p.m.

1157
01:38:17,042 --> 01:38:18,167
Where to?

1158
01:38:18,250 --> 01:38:19,333
The market.

1159
01:38:19,417 --> 01:38:21,792
<i>She went to the market in my rickshaw.</i>

1160
01:38:21,875 --> 01:38:23,750
<i>I took her there.</i>

1161
01:38:24,792 --> 01:38:27,042
<i>I saw her walking around the market.</i>

1162
01:38:29,542 --> 01:38:30,542
<i>I waited.</i>

1163
01:38:32,375 --> 01:38:35,250
<i>And then I drove her back.</i>

1164
01:38:36,542 --> 01:38:39,333
<i>I saw her feed mutton to the dogs.</i>

1165
01:38:39,417 --> 01:38:41,542
Suddenly… there was a loud explosion.

1166
01:38:43,208 --> 01:38:44,833
Madam was outside the house.

1167
01:38:44,917 --> 01:38:46,167
How could she murder…

1168
01:38:46,750 --> 01:38:47,958
She couldn't, right?

1169
01:38:48,042 --> 01:38:50,125
You scoundrel!
Looks to me like you're the murderer!

1170
01:38:50,792 --> 01:38:52,333
Mess with me and I'll break your legs.

1171
01:38:52,417 --> 01:38:55,000
You'll be riding a rickshaw with one leg.

1172
01:38:55,083 --> 01:38:57,083
-Get lost.
-Buzz off.

1173
01:38:57,167 --> 01:38:59,125
Everyone has a different
version of the story.

1174
01:39:00,250 --> 01:39:02,417
What beats me is, when there
was so much drama going on here,

1175
01:39:02,500 --> 01:39:04,875
why would she leave
the husband and lover alone at home

1176
01:39:06,167 --> 01:39:08,417
and go to the market?

1177
01:39:08,917 --> 01:39:11,750
Perhaps to hide the murder weapon, sir?

1178
01:39:11,833 --> 01:39:12,875
Where is it?

1179
01:39:15,042 --> 01:39:16,292
When did she hide it and where?

1180
01:39:18,083 --> 01:39:21,500
I am convinced
that this woman is behind it all.

1181
01:39:22,583 --> 01:39:24,292
She's just leading us
on a wild goose chase.

1182
01:39:28,667 --> 01:39:29,583
Hello?

1183
01:39:30,667 --> 01:39:32,042
What?

1184
01:39:38,917 --> 01:39:39,750
Hello, sir.

1185
01:39:41,333 --> 01:39:43,292
What did you find, Mr. Singh?

1186
01:39:45,833 --> 01:39:47,042
See this, sir.

1187
01:39:47,125 --> 01:39:49,125
The blast took place
during the Clean India campaign.

1188
01:39:49,208 --> 01:39:50,583
We were recording that.

1189
01:39:50,667 --> 01:39:52,000
And here is Neel.

1190
01:39:58,167 --> 01:39:59,042
Oh.

1191
01:40:00,500 --> 01:40:01,667
So here he is.

1192
01:40:01,750 --> 01:40:02,833
See the replay, sir.

1193
01:40:03,917 --> 01:40:06,292
We've been searching
for the lover all this while…

1194
01:40:06,375 --> 01:40:08,792
And here he is, swimming away!

1195
01:40:10,333 --> 01:40:12,583
When you guys were busy recording videos,

1196
01:40:12,667 --> 01:40:14,542
