1229
01:41:39,667 --> 01:41:41,917
Take her inside and get her to talk.

1230
01:41:42,417 --> 01:41:45,000
What were you saying, huh?

1231
01:41:45,542 --> 01:41:46,833
Madness in love…

1232
01:41:46,917 --> 01:41:49,167
