1233
01:41:49,708 --> 01:41:51,625
Madness, huh?

1234
01:41:55,208 --> 01:41:56,792
<i>What else does Dinesh Pandit write, huh?</i>

1235
01:41:56,875 --> 01:41:58,042
<i>Tell me!</i>

1236
01:41:58,125 --> 01:41:59,708
<i>What else does he say?</i>

1237
01:42:04,375 --> 01:42:07,917
Sir. She's an adamant one.

1238
01:42:08,542 --> 01:42:11,917
Even though I thrashed her,
she hasn't spilled anything.

1239
01:42:13,875 --> 01:42:17,125
Ask the technician if he can do
the lie detector test tomorrow.

1240
01:42:17,208 --> 01:42:19,000
-Okay, sir.
-Listen.

1241
01:42:20,208 --> 01:42:21,083
Yes?

1242
01:42:22,125 --> 01:42:23,042
Let her go.

1243
01:42:24,583 --> 01:42:25,500
Okay.

1244
01:42:30,125 --> 01:42:32,750
Hey! Rani, get up.

1245
01:43:02,917 --> 01:43:03,958
Madam?

1246
01:43:13,917 --> 01:43:15,625
Why is it taking so long?

1247
01:43:23,958 --> 01:43:26,708
Why don't I take you
to the doctor tomorrow?

1248
01:43:28,000 --> 01:43:30,542
I need to go back
to the police station tomorrow.

1249
01:43:44,458 --> 01:43:45,917
Is everything ready, Mishra?

1250
01:43:46,000 --> 01:43:47,708
The recordings are precise.

1251
01:43:47,792 --> 01:43:49,500
There's no chance of a mistake.

1252
01:43:50,667 --> 01:43:51,792
Please come in.

1253
01:43:52,375 --> 01:43:54,292
This machine detects every minute detail,

1254
01:43:55,167 --> 01:43:58,583
perspiration, trembling of lips,
eye movement.

1255
01:43:58,667 --> 01:43:59,500
All these get noted.

1256
01:44:00,000 --> 01:44:01,917
Your heartbeat is being monitored, anyway.

1257
01:44:04,125 --> 01:44:05,792
