1259
01:44:17,708 --> 01:44:19,208
Hurry up.

1260
01:44:19,792 --> 01:44:21,708
How long will you take?

1261
01:44:21,792 --> 01:44:23,042
Come on out!

1262
01:44:23,708 --> 01:44:24,708
Rani!

1263
01:44:25,375 --> 01:44:26,917
